<br>
The military guys do get them turned in, in time. However, getting mail out of or in to is a military vessel or unit is not and cannot be a priority.<br>
<br>
The “Idiots” don’t postmark their own mail and their mail is not postmarked until it can be offloaded from the ship. <br>
