It isn’t that the military “Neglects” to follow standard postal procedures. Standard postal procedures do not take the militaries needs into consideration. Anyone with any insight in military procedures and operations knows it is logistically impossible to hold military personal abroad accountable to the same rules (Postal/tax/whatever) as people living inside US borders.<br>
<br>
